# Re-include the brand asset directory. Some users' global
# .gitignore has the macOS-Finder pattern "Icon?" which matches
# our "icons" directory case-insensitively and silently strips
# the entire PWA / favicon / OG bundle from commits. Force it
# back in here.
!public/icons
!public/icons/**
tests/visual/out/
